This is a python app that captures screenshots of the user's screen at regular intervals and logs the descriptions of the screenshots to a file.

It's a WIP project.

Currently the user can pause the process and ask questions about the log.

The user can also clear the log and reset.

The user can also exit the program.


Future features:

Voice chat with the AI.

Active assistance from the AI if it determines that the user is in need of help.

Active search in the background for stuff the user might need.

Active idea generation for creative solutions or alternative solutions to problems.
